Features that should be implemented

---------- Video ------------

// Upload & Processing

- Video upload with progress tracking
- Automatic video encoding (HLS, MP4)
- Thumbnail generation
- Video metadata extraction (duration, resolution)
- Content validation (format, size, length)

// Publishing

- Draft/Published states
- Scheduled publishing
- Unpublishing/archiving
- Version control (if updates)

// Browsing

- Paginated video listing
- Category/tag filtering
- Sorting (newest, popular, price)
- Search (title, description, transcripts)

// Organization

- Video categorization
- Playlist creation
- Video recommendations
- Featured videos
- Trending videos

// Streaming

- Adaptive bitrate streaming (HLS/DASH)
- Multiple quality options (360p, 720p, 1080p)
- Playback speed control
- Subtitles/closed captions
- Audio tracks selection

// Player Features

- Continue watching
- Bookmark positions
- Picture-in-picture
- AirPlay/Chromecast
- Offline download (if supported)

// Engagement

- View count tracking
- Watch time analytics
- Completion rates
- Drop-off points
- Re-watch statistics

// Performance

- Buffer rate monitoring
- Quality switches
- Playback errors
- Load times

// Associated Content

- Video descriptions
- Chapters/timestamps
- Attachments (PDFs, links)
- Quizzes/assessments
- Discussion/comments

// Metadata

- Transcripts
- Keywords/tags
- Age ratings
- Content warnings
- Accessibility features

-------------------- USER --------------------------
// Personal Information

- Full name, bio, avatar
- Contact information
- Social media links
- Professional background

// Profile Customization

- Theme preferences (light/dark mode)
- Notification preferences
- Language settings
- Accessibility settings

// User-Generated Content

- User reviews & ratings
- Discussion posts/comments
- Questions asked/answered
- Study notes/annotations
  
  -------------------------- ANALITICs -------------------------------

// Real-time event tracking

- Track user actions (clicks, views, searches)
- Track video engagement (play, pause, completion)
- Track purchase events (add to cart, checkout)
- Track system performance (errors, load times)

// Session tracking

- User session recording
- Page view tracking
- User flow analysis
- Device/browser tracking

// Custom event tracking

- Business-specific events
- Funnel tracking
- Goal completion tracking

// Interactive dashboards

- Executive dashboard (KPIs overview)
- Video performance dashboard
- User engagement dashboard
- Revenue dashboard
- Real-time activity dashboard

// Chart types

- Line charts (trends over time)
- Bar charts (comparisons)
- Pie charts (distributions)
- Heat maps (user activity)
- Funnel visualization

// Custom reports

- Drag-and-drop report builder
