- Scheduled report delivery
- Export to PDF/Excel

// Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

- Revenue metrics (MRR, ARR, LTV)
- User metrics (DAU, MAU, churn rate)
- Video metrics (views, engagement, completion)
- Conversion metrics (signup rate, purchase rate)

// Trend analysis

- Time series analysis
- Seasonality detection
- Growth rate calculation
- Comparative analysis (vs previous period)

// Segmentation

- User segmentation (by behavior, demographics)
- Cohort analysis
- RFM analysis (Recency, Frequency, Monetary)
- CLV prediction

// Predictive analytics

- Churn prediction
- Revenue forecasting
- User lifetime value prediction
- Content recommendation scoring

// Anomaly detection

- Automatic outlier detection
- Pattern deviation alerts
- Fraud detection
- System performance anomalies

// A/B testing

- Experiment setup and tracking
- Statistical significance calculation
- Multivariate testing
- Conversion rate optimization

// Automated alerts

- KPI threshold alerts
- Anomaly detection alerts
- System downtime alerts
- Business event alerts

// Notification channels

- Email notifications
- Slack/Teams integration
- SMS alerts
- In-app notifications

// Alert management

- Alert prioritization
- Alert grouping
